Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.51,0:01:32.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭這個城市
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.59,0:01:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭家
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.28,0:01:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭父母
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.42,0:01:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也討厭父母的責備
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.23,0:01:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更討厭他們一有空就責罵我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.64,0:01:42.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厭了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.79,0:01:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓這一切 都去見鬼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.34,0:01:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天我都這麼想著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.44,0:01:52.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如之前向大家報道的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.89,0:01:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天15點46分左右
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.64,0:01:58.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以關東為中心的一帶發生了大地震
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.20,0:02:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該次地震的震源位於東京灣北部
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.62,0:02:05.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,震源深度約為25公里
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.65,0:02:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從地震的規模來看預計達到裡氏8.0
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.52,0:02:13.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請注意餘震及海嘯的危險
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:16.32,title1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(960,660)\fad(500,0)}「台場、陷落」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.59,0:02:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小野澤同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.97,0:02:16.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小野澤未來同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.68,0:02:17.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.52,0:02:23.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好下一個 加籐同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.42,0:02:24.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.68,0:02:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我看看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.55,0:02:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久保同學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.45,0:02:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.95,0:02:29.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久保真弓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.20,0:02:32.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 成績
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.63,0:02:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慘不忍睹
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.18,0:02:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.09,0:02:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難兄難弟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.16,0:02:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也拿不出手了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.03,0:02:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家管的很嚴 夏天的旅遊可能泡湯了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.29,0:02:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別愁啦 由佳
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.10,0:02:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有討厭自己孩子的父母嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.34,0:02:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.56,0:02:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去加勒比啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.10,0:02:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年打算過得休閒一點
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.17,0:02:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨紗去哪兒度假?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.16,0:02:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加拿大 爸爸蓋了座木屋
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.84,0:03:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 今天來我家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.76,0:03:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽要做蛋奶酥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.72,0:03:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.95,0:03:08.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小惠家離學校這麼近 真好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.90,0:03:13.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小野澤暑假裡打算去哪兒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.24,0:03:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家沒有這樣的安排啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.99,0:03:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那還是選個涼快的地方好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:22.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年好像會很熱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.00,0:03:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面 關於這次的暑假作業
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.82,0:03:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請展望一下十年後的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.28,0:03:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後把它寫成一份未來報告
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.54,0:03:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用這個暑假的充裕時間 好好思考一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.19,0:03:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.55,0:03:42.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.32,0:03:44.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見 byebye
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.26,0:03:46.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那個你準備怎麼寫?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.24,0:03:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來報告?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.78,0:03:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無頭緒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由佳不是有嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.35,0:03:52.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼琴家什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.49,0:03:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鋼琴是喜歡啦 不過沒那麼容易呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.36,0:03:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有喜歡的就不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.13,0:04:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 我連想幹什麼想說什麼都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.35,0:04:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:06.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 去趟涉谷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.61,0:04:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 未來一起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.78,0:04:11.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去不了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.19,0:04:15.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天父母上班 要跟弟弟一起看家
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.15,0:04:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天開始放暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.61,0:04:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實也無所謂啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.86,0:04:40.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼特別期待的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得剪劉海了 留著礙事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒什麼未來的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.21,0:05:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我死也不要變成那種大人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十年後的我應該不會那樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.70,0:05:27.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.94,0:05:30.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.37,0:05:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.96,0:05:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手機大聖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.69,0:05:37.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次看見手機大聖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.61,0:05:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她要發火了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.94,0:05:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你亂說什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.11,0:05:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小野澤啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.39,0:05:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中學生活怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.28,0:05:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會一般呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.61,0:05:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很一般啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.03,0:05:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師你們在幹嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.02,0:05:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠貴要我幫忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.88,0:06:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸送給我的七葉樹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.77,0:06:03.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放家里長不大所以拿到學校來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師說可以把它種在那兒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.25,0:06:10.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 姐姐也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.15,0:06:13.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.33,0:06:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.61,0:06:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 全是泥巴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.49,0:06:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偶爾流點汗也不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.18,0:06:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.74,0:06:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能長大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.37,0:06:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 謝謝你 一樹
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.77,0:06:31.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暑假的時候一起來澆水吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.94,0:06:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.76,0:06:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家吧悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:36.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.08,0:06:39.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說好種完了踢球的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:40.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.96,0:06:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 那傢伙怎麼這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.20,0:07:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.01,0:07:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.41,0:07:09.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹說聲我回來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.55,0:07:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為是小偷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:14.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要走了 客戶們等著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.04,0:07:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是蛋糕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.83,0:07:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怕我們不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.16,0:07:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽得走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.78,0:07:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記得也讓悠貴吃蛋糕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽在減肥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.46,0:07:40.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三角形的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.71,0:07:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼不買圓的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.30,0:07:44.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 哦對了未來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下記得收衣服 好像要下雨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.50,0:07:50.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完蛋糕把碟子洗了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:53.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外再接一下包裹和賬單
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.87,0:07:55.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新鮮的東西記得放冰箱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:07:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我七點回來 拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.09,0:08:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成績單拿出來 我回來看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.34,0:08:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉唆一大堆 誰鳥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.96,0:08:21.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:23.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給媽媽的 生日嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祝你生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.84,0:08:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般啦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.89,0:08:42.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.15,0:08:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.80,0:08:47.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐送什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.26,0:08:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 無所謂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.34,0:08:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們一起送給她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.08,0:08:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你畫的嗎 你自己送吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.46,0:09:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有蛋糕 吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.01,0:09:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.14,0:09:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.26,0:09:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.85,0:09:15.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跟媽媽一起吃就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.42,0:09:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「媽媽得走啦　記得也讓悠貴吃蛋糕哦」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.02,0:09:21.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「媽媽在減肥呢」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.55,0:09:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真像
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.01,0:09:26.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.89,0:09:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是長不大 悠貴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.80,0:09:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 好想吃圓形蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.00,0:09:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生日蛋糕竟然不是圓的 太隨意了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.51,0:09:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 這個好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下 現在超忙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.43,0:09:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了 手機大聖
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.19,0:09:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家裡好涼快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.94,0:09:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.95,0:10:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.60,0:10:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.51,0:10:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 我先洗個澡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.98,0:10:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎 今天是媽媽生日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.46,0:10:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.29,0:10:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.61,0:10:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 東西都灑到地上了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.59,0:10:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快收拾一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.80,0:10:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啦 明天放暑假了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.27,0:10:36.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 作業要早點做完
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.88,0:10:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說這個啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.75,0:10:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們家不去哪兒旅遊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.58,0:10:44.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老是考試考試的 哪兒都沒去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.98,0:10:48.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是 問問媽媽看如何
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.96,0:10:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.95,0:10:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她老是動不動就發火
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能現在比較忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.19,0:10:58.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等有空了再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.77,0:11:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.28,0:11:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.96,0:11:09.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.88,0:11:12.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記買牛奶了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.82,0:11:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.98,0:11:14.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.01,0:11:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在就熱
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.56,0:11:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八點多了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.14,0:11:22.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那有什麼辦法 我也有工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.01,0:11:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我想孩子們可能餓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.25,0:11:27.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在熱了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.68,0:11:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你們有完沒完
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.00,0:11:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸也別老拿事往我們身上推
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.13,0:11:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在鬱悶什麼哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.13,0:11:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮物…沒能送出去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.33,0:11:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太照顧父母了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.21,0:11:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明還是個小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.99,0:12:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己不也還是個小孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.50,0:12:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你也覺得爸爸和媽媽和好比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.89,0:12:08.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事已至此 隨他們去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.86,0:12:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹啥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.21,0:12:22.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.85,0:12:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讓爸媽看了我的未來報告
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.61,0:12:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是就開始教育我先去上大學
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家也是 叫我鋼琴課不要偷懶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.75,0:12:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.63,0:12:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想成為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.33,0:12:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算讓我寫未來也…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.20,0:12:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.79,0:13:03.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.31,0:13:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.82,0:13:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見啦 我走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:11.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.30,0:13:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別任性啦小悠 媽媽有工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.36,0:13:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.91,0:13:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我和姐姐兩個人去如何?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:21.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.17,0:13:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.63,0:13:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 機器人展?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.01,0:13:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在台場開展
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.32,0:13:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能帶他去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.23,0:13:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要去什麼機器人展啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.80,0:13:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說為什麼非要我照顧悠貴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.62,0:13:39.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.18,0:13:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.53,0:13:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正是暑假
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.37,0:13:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己還任性的說不去暑假補習班
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.56,0:13:46.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正很空吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.18,0:13:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.71,0:13:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我帶他去就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.18,0:13:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶他去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.33,0:14:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 快看啊 大橋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.48,0:14:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前來也來過吧 快看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.35,0:14:05.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.07,0:14:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一站 台場
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.77,0:14:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,台場到了 下車了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.42,0:14:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 我們乘公車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.06,0:14:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是你說在台場開展 才早下了一站吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.61,0:14:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍忍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.27,0:14:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點不熱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.38,0:14:46.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.56,0:14:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.70,0:15:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這嗎 你想看的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.48,0:15:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 你不喜歡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.57,0:15:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐快看 可以摸哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.85,0:15:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.78,0:15:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 握手 握手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.36,0:15:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  那裡的可以操作哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.35,0:15:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些四足機器人是可以進行自由移動的四足機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.58,0:15:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四個腳分別能夠適應不同高低位置
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.90,0:16:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠在災害地區凹凸不平處安全自由移動
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.63,0:16:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.51,0:16:04.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你也試試
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.03,0:16:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快啊 好快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.48,0:16:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 你這麼亂來的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.21,0:16:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.27,0:16:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 你們要玩到啥時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.92,0:16:28.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不能輪到我們麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.79,0:16:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.14,0:17:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 我們一起買個禮物給媽媽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.94,0:17:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 還是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.91,0:17:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果她和我們一起來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:14.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不會遇到這種不高興的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.07,0:17:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小孩子肯定會被欺負的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.66,0:17:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 我也沒錢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.23,0:17:22.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有哦 錢的話
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.95,0:17:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 哪個好?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.60,0:17:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.25,0:17:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個很有人氣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.62,0:17:51.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個偶爾帶帶也不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.39,0:18:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.77,0:18:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是想要這個嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.75,0:18:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.39,0:18:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 這個對我家婆婆來說果然是太花哨了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:12.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.97,0:18:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別客氣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了啦 真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.71,0:18:21.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 這個呢 這個不錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.29,0:18:23.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選禮物嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.63,0:18:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.21,0:18:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽要過生日了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.71,0:18:31.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好呢 我要是收到女兒這樣的禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會感動落淚的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.97,0:18:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽能開心就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.12,0:18:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.36,0:18:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天人很多 不要迷路了哦 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.37,0:18:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把我當小孩啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.51,0:18:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 就選這個吧 媽媽很喜歡花的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.31,0:18:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨便你啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.59,0:18:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 我去下廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.88,0:19:00.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.50,0:19:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 拿一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.98,0:19:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 順便買點飲料來吧 我在外面等你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.82,0:19:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.59,0:19:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.43,0:19:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 能不能不要傻站在出入口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.78,0:19:34.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.33,0:19:38.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼都是些讓人心煩的事啊
