Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.04,0:19:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1230,855)}咨詢處
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.83,0:19:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都是些不開心的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.22,0:19:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.57,0:19:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.65,0:19:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那什麼表情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.54,0:20:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的人生 將來會有好事發生嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.91,0:20:13.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了 什麼都好麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆 讓這種世界毀滅掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.43,0:20:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地震?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.23,0:20:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
